      FileContext fields, rule wiring, conventions, local link workflow.

**DX14: Workspace/monorepo guide is missing**
- README: "run from specific scope directory", but no full workflow example
  (init, configure, share deps, CI/CD).
- [x] DONE 2026-06-13: docs/MONOREPO_GUIDE.md — layout, per-scope vs shared,
      credentials across scopes, CI matrix, tips.

**DX15: MCP integration docs have hardcoded paths and are thin**
- The MCP quickstart contains `/Users/Ivan.Baev/Development/...` in examples.
- No explanation of what auto-pull is, why, and when to disable it.
- [x] Update with $HOME substitution — DONE 2026-06-13: mcp-quickstart.md now uses
      `<SYNCRONA_REPO>`/`<SCOPE_PROJECT>` placeholders and placeholder credentials
      (also removed committed real-looking creds: work email + password + instance),
      and points at `syncrona login` instead of inline env vars.
- [x] Document auto-pull and MCP startup troubleshooting — DONE 2026-06-13: added an "Auto-pull on startup" + troubleshooting section to docs/mcp-quickstart.md (default on, SYNCRONA_MCP_AUTO_PULL_ALL_SCOPES=0 to disable, runs after connect).
- [x] Repo hygiene: DONE 2026-06-21 — removed internal scratch/planning docs
      (fixes.md, docs/syncrona-plan.md, docs/desktop-app-plan.md,
      docs/github-title-page.md, docs/npm-title-page.md).

